    "body" : "<p>You can clean cache in React Native >= 0.50 and npm > 5 :</p>\n\n<pre><code>watchman watch-del-all &amp;&amp; \nrm -rf $TMPDIR/react-native-packager-cache-* &amp;&amp;\nrm -rf $TMPDIR/metro-bundler-cache-* &amp;&amp; \nrm -rf node_modules/ \n&amp;&amp; npm cache clean --force &amp;&amp;\nnpm install &amp;&amp; \nnpm start -- --reset-cache\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Apart from cleaning npm cache you might need to <a href=\"https://medium.com/@abhisheknalwaya/how-to-clear-react-native-cache-c435c258834e\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">reset simulator or clean build</a> etc.</p>\n"
