    "body" : "<p>If you are using <code>WebStorm</code>, press configuration selection drop down button left of the run button and select edit configurations:</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/5Ypl1.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/5Ypl1.png\" alt=\"edit configurations\"></a></p>\n\n<p>Double click on <code>Start React Native Bundler</code> at bottom in <code>Before launch</code> section:</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/13Bq3.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/13Bq3.png\" alt=\"before launch\"></a></p>\n\n<p>Enter <code>--reset-cache</code> to <code>Arguments</code> section:</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/3vaAR.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/3vaAR.png\" alt=\"arguments\"></a></p>\n"
  }, {
