    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I know it's too late to reply but it might help someone:</p>\n<p>In case you just want to clear cache just hit this command</p>\n<pre><code>npm cache clean --force\n</code></pre>\n<hr />\n<p>Happy coding :)</p>\n<hr />\n"
