    "question_id" : 46878638,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I solved my react-native cache problem by this way:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>open terminal, then <code>cd 'your project root path'</code></li>\n<li>execute this command: <code>npm start -- --reset-cache</code></li>\n<li>open your react native project, If the first run doesn't work, you may need to run it again.</li>\n</ol>\n"
